{"tid":1428302,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好少開post  希望大家入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:38:36.000Z","uid":57003,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02cf7cdef4562e60a9f11bc8cb45f6aeacbad353","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"其實而家正苦既玩法好明顯係轉移焦點<br />\n<br />\n想廣大民眾focus係我地同班狗度，從而令正苦既所有不公條例被淡忘<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以專注係香港所有不公平條例 而唔淨止班狗<br />\n<br />\n狗 我地就撚硬 一定要唱撚衰佢地 但係唔係最大焦點<br />\n<br />\n而家班狗已經人神共憤 過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候轉返個焦點返黎 去返條例同義士度 而唔係淨係同班狗作戰<br />\n<br />\n柒婆放大假 + 每日由班狗開記招 就係好好既證明<br />\n<br />\n而家全世界望住我地 唔係要睇我地打狗 係要睇香港點樣比柒婆成班人出賣！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 大家努力"},{"pid":"321677f409a855657fe53a9fe857b085ca753ebf","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6d6cfdd3e87ef548de11adc95554448c304d86a","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b57a09240016acc55cec01ef40c964c5ac4115d","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b65153a80cb901218d3d84b6dd77c6684decf070","tid":1428302,"uid":188058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"e9515ea755d9821f13da7ef8a833f16a794cceaa","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02565b12e6e9e6830762c000113216c16101907c","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"最後一推"},{"pid":"a2cd31994f49537de8511d4f25b13b1f5a45f5c0","tid":1428302,"uid":301006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a849f8dccbc6f072533e931ce0d60e1f4bb5ef6","tid":1428302,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":0